{
  "name": "custom-language-config",
  "displayName": "Custom Language Config",
  "version": "0.0.0",
  "private": true,
  "description": "",
  "categories": [
    "Formatters",
    "Linters",
    "Other",
    "Programming Languages"
  ],
  "keywords": [
    "configuration",
    "custom",
    "formatter",
    "language",
    "language server",
    "lsp"
  ],
  "license": "MIT",
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "https://github.com/CatBraaain/custom-language-config"
  },
  "publisher": "CatBraaain",
  "type": "module",
  "main": "./dist/index.js",
  "scripts": {
    "compile": "vp pack",
    "package": "vsce package",
    "pretest": "bun run compile",
    "test": "vp test",
    "test:performance": "bun run ./dist/test/performanceTest.js",
    "vscode:prepublish": "bun run compile"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "jsonc-parser": "^3.2.0",
    "string-argv": "^0.3.2",
    "vscode-languageclient": "^9.0.1"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "@types/node": "^20.0.0",
    "@types/vscode": "^1.85.0",
    "@vscode/test-electron": "^2.3.0",
    "@vscode/vsce": "^2.19.0",
    "typescript": "^5.0.0",
    "vite-plus": "^0.1.20"
  },
  "contributes": {
    "commands": [
      {
        "command": "unifiedLanguageConfig.manualRestartLSP",
        "title": "Manual Restart LSP",
        "category": "Unified Language Config"
      }
    ],
    "configuration": {
      "title": "Unified Language Config",
      "properties": {
        "customLanguageConfig.rules": {
          "type": "array",
          "default": [],
          "description": "Rule-based configuration - Apply LSP, formatter, and language properties based on conditions",
          "items": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "when": {
                "type": "object",
                "description": "Conditions for rule application",
                "properties": {
                  "langs": {
                    "type": "array",
                    "items": {
                      "type": "string"
                    },
                    "description": "Target language IDs (applies to all languages if not specified)"
                  },
                  "required": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "description": "Required file and pattern conditions",
                    "properties": {
                      "file": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "description": "Required file regex pattern (e.g., package\\.json, tsconfig\\.json)"
                      },
                      "contains": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "description": "Pattern that must be contained in the file (regex)"
                      }
                    },
                    "required": [
                      "file"
                    ]
                  }
                }
              },
              "use": {
                "type": "object",
                "description": "Settings to apply when conditions match",
                "properties": {
                  "lsp": {
                    "type": "array",
                    "items": {
                      "type": "string"
                    },
                    "description": "Array of LSP server commands"
                  },
                  "formatter": {
                    "type": "array",
                    "items": {
                      "type": "string"
                    },
                    "description": "Array of formatter commands"
                  },
                  "langConfig": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "description": "Language properties configuration",
                    "properties": {
                      "comments": {
                        "type": "object",
                        "properties": {
                          "lineComment": {
                            "type": "string"
                          },
                          "blockComment": {
                            "type": "array",
                            "items": {
                              "type": "string"
                            },
                            "minItems": 2,
                            "maxItems": 2
                          }
                        }
                      },
                      "brackets": {
                        "type": "array",
                        "items": {
                          "type": "array",
                          "items": {
                            "type": "string"
                          },
                          "minItems": 2,
                          "maxItems": 2
                        }
                      },
                      "autoClosingPairs": {
                        "type": "array",
                        "items": {
                          "type": "object",
                          "properties": {
                            "open": {
                              "type": "string"
                            },
                            "close": {
                              "type": "string"
                            }
                          },
                          "required": [
                            "open",
                            "close"
                          ]
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            "required": [
              "when",
              "use"
            ]
          }
        },
        "customLanguageConfig.logLevel": {
          "type": "string",
          "enum": [
            "debug",
            "info",
            "warn",
            "error",
            "critical"
          ],
          "default": "info",
          "markdownDescription": "Log level for the extension output\n\n- **debug**: Detailed diagnostic information\n- **info**: General informational messages (default)\n- **warn**: Warning messages\n- **error**: Error messages\n- **critical**: Critical errors only\n\n**ログレベル**:\n- **debug**: 詳細な診断情報\n- **info**: 一般的な情報メッセージ (デフォルト)\n- **warn**: 警告メッセージ\n- **error**: エラーメッセージ\n- **critical**: 重大なエラーのみ"
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "activationEvents": [
    "onStartupFinished"
  ],
  "engines": {
    "vscode": "^1.85.0"
  }
}
